N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 438.3 - State urban cultural park system projects

State Regulations
A development project undertaken in a State-owned
environmental, cultural or recreational facility or site, which is within a
designated urban cultural park and identified in an approved management plan, shall be eligible for funding. Notes
